        "readme": "<h1>Calypso UI</h1>\n<p>BlueOS extension for the DeepEx Calypso ROV control interface.</p>\n<p>The extension provides the vehicle dashboard, power SCADA, telemetry widgets, mission logging, video stream display, sonar controls, diagnostics, and setup tools used by the Calypso UI backend.</p>",
